util

Class SubTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.SubTree

  • public class SubTree
extends java.lang.Object
    A Class, which Objects represent a Range of Stats, that an Item might occur with. This isn't complete, as there might be other SubTrees for a single Item, so this is just a part of the MultiBonus for the Item.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Haeldeus
